---
import Layout from '../../layouts/AGS.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/AGS/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../components/AGS/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="AltiesGaming" description="Information on AltiesGamingStudios' AltiesGaming Youtube channel">
	<Header 
		subtitle="AltiesGaming"
	/>
	
	<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-dark-subtle navbar-dark">
		<div class="container-fluid">
			<ul class="navbar-nav">
				<li class="nav-item">
					<a class="nav-link" href="./">Home</a>
				</li>
				<li class="nav-item">
					<a class="nav-link active" href="./AG">AltiesGaming</a>
				</li>
				<li class="nav-item">
					<a class="nav-link" href="./AGL">AltiesGamingLive</a>
				</li>
				<li class="nav-item dropdown">
					<a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
						More
					</a>
					<ul class="dropdown-menu">
						<li><a class="dropdown-item" href="./FEAT">Featured content</a></li>
						<li><a class="dropdown-item" href="./FAQ">FAQ</a></li>
						<li><a class="dropdown-item" href="./Discord">Discord</a></li>
						<li><a class="dropdown-item" href="./Retired">Retired Content</a></li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li class="nav-item">
					<a class="nav-link" href="/">Hub</a>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</nav>
	<div class="container mt-5">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-4">
				<h3 class="mt-4">Main Pages</h3>
				<ul class="nav nav-pills flex-column">
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link" href="./">Home</a>
					</li>
					<li class="nav-item">
							<a class="nav-link active" href="./AG">AltiesGaming</a>
						</li>
						<li class="nav-item">
							<a class="nav-link" href="./AGL">AltiesGamingLive</a>
						</li>
				</ul>
				<hr class="d-sm-none">
				<div class="ratio ratio-1x1 clearfix">
					<iframe src="https://ptb.discord.com/widget?id=757341031741128802&theme=dark" allowtransparency="true" sandbox="allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts"></iframe>
			</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-8">
				<h2>About AltiesGaming</h2>
				<h6>What is AltiesGaming?</h6>
				<p>AltiesGaming is altie's First channel started in 2017</p>
				<h6>Why did Altie's Gaming switch to Minecraft only? And why did AltiesGaming switch back to any game?</h6>
				<p>AltiesGaming switched to only minecraft to, as quoted from the old website;</p>
				<h5>"<code>AltiesGaming switched to only Minecraft content on Oct 20, 2021 because it is way easier to make one type of content than multiple. It also helps you build a commuinity because viewers know what to expect when coming back to your channel!</code>"</h5>
				<p>And we switched back to any game on <code>June 27, 2023</code>, this is because although it is more unpredictable for viewers, it makes it easier to make and post videos more regularly.</p>

				<h2 class="mt-5">Channel</h2>
				<h5>AltiesGaming</h5>
				<ul class="list-group">
					<li class="list-group-item list-group-item-secondary">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-4">Channel <span class=" top-0 float-end badge rounded-pill bg-danger">Sub Count</span></div>
							<div class="col-4">Channel disc</div>
							<div class="col-4">To the Channel</div>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="list-group-item list-group-item-info">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-4">AltiesGaming <span class=" top-0 float-end badge rounded-pill bg-danger" id="AGsubs">API Unavailable</span></div>
							<div class="col-4">Main Channel, Mostly Minecraft Content</div>
							<div class="col-4">
								<div class="btn-group" role="group">
									<a class="btn btn-youtube" href="https://www.youtube.com/@altiesgaming">YouTube</a>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<br />
	<div class="container-fluid text-center">
		<h2>Recomended Video</h2>
		<h4>from AltiesGaming</h4>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col">
				<div class="ratio ratio-16x9">
					<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/FZK13YrjThA" allowfullscreen></iframe>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<br />
	<div class="container">
	<h2>Videos:</h2>
	<p>We are working on getting a full list of videos made!</p>
	</div>
	<br />
	<script src="/JS/sub-AG.js" is:inline></script>
	<Footer />
</Layout>
<style>
	.btn-youtube {
		background-color: #FF0000;
		color: #FFFFFF;
	}
	.btn-twitch {
		background-color: rgb(145, 70, 255);
		color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
	}
</style>
